HTTP	Response	Codes		
Response	code				Description		
200		Request	processed	successfully		
400		Bad	request		
401		Unauthorized	request		
403		Request	is	forbidden		
404		The	request	resource	is	not	found		
500		Internal	Host	Error		
503		Service	unavailable		
 
 
Production	Requirements	
A	duly	signed	request	letter,	template	is	available	on	the	documentation	section	of	the	
API	on	the	developer	portal.	Send	the	letter	to	buni@kcbgroup.com	
	
For	any	additional	support,	please	write	to	buni@kcbgroup.com	